<p> <b>Collection of Information :</b> </p>
<p><b>1. Information You Provide:</b> We collect information you provide directly to us, such as when you create an account, update your profile, post content, or contact customer support.</p>
<p><b>2. Information We Collect Automatically:</b> When you use our services, we automatically collect information including, but not limited to, usage details, IP addresses, and information collected through cookies and other tracking technologies.</p>
<p><b>3. Information from Third Parties:</b> We may receive information about you from third parties, including our business partners and service providers.</p>
<p> <b>Use of Information :<p> </b>
<p>The information we collect is used to provide, maintain, and improve our services, to develop new services, and to protect YouPost and our users. We also use the information to communicate with you about products, services, offers, promotions, and events offered by YouPost and others.<p>
<p> <b>Sharing of Information :<p> </b>
<p><b>1. With Your Consent:</b> We may share information with companies, organizations, or individuals outside of YouPost when we have your consent to do so.</p>
<p><b>2. With Tangent Computers:</b> As a subsidiary of Tangent Computers, YouPost shares information with its parent company. Tangent Computers may use this information to help operate, provide, improve, understand, customize, support, and market our services.</p>
<p><b>3. For Legal Reasons:</b> We will share personal information outside of YouPost if we have a good-faith belief that access, use, preservation, or disclosure of the information is reasonably necessary to meet any applicable law, regulation, legal process, or enforceable governmental request.</p>
<p> <b>Your Choices :<p> </b>
